        <value>
          <label>forge clans</label>
        </value>
        <success>Always</success>
        <MayRequire>VanillaExpanded.VMemesE</MayRequire>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/IdeoPresetDef[defName="VME_Dwarven_Artificers"]/description</xpath>
        <value>
          <description>No day is better spent than one in a hot forge. With hammers, kilns, and scrap steel, we turn hidden workshops into the backbone of a hard underground life.</description>
        </value>
        <success>Always</success>
        <MayRequire>VanillaExpanded.VMemesE</MayRequire>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/IdeoPresetDef[defName="VME_Medieval_Monarchists"]/label</xpath>
        <value>
          <label>feudal overlords</label>
        </value>
        <success>Always</success>
        <MayRequire>VanillaExpanded.VMemesE</MayRequire>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/IdeoPresetDef[defName="VME_Medieval_Monarchists"]/description</xpath>
        <value>
          <description>Our forebears survived by following warlords, bosses, and local strongmen, and we see no reason to change now. If neighboring settlements prefer blades and tribute, then tribute is what they will pay.</description>
        </value>
        <success>Always</success>
        <MayRequire>VanillaExpanded.VMemesE</MayRequire>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/IdeoPresetDef[defName="VME_Eastern_Revivalists"]/label</xpath>
        <value>
          <label>old-world revivalists</label>
        </value>
        <success>Always</success>
        <MayRequire>VanillaExpanded.VMemesE</MayRequire>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/IdeoPresetDef[defName="VME_Eastern_Revivalists"]/description</xpath>
        <value>
          <description>We believe the old world still holds lessons worth reviving. Discipline, ritual, and a sharpened blade keep a people alive when former brothers turn on each other.</description>
        </value>
        <success>Always</success>
        <MayRequire>VanillaExpanded.VMemesE</MayRequire>
      </li>
